'''全球華人反邪教聯盟'''（Chinese Anti-Cult World Alliance）是一個由美籍華人創立的反[[法輪功|法輪功]]組織。該組織認為法輪功是[[邪教|邪教]]，並且損害了中國人在海外的形象<ref name=Kil2011>{{cite web|url=https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/03/07/a-battle-for-chinese-hearts-and-minds-in-flushing/|title=A Battle for Chinese Hearts and Minds in Flushing|author=Corey Kilgannon|publisher=New York Times|date=2011-03-07|accessdate=2017-02-01|archive-date=2018-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203181555/https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/03/07/a-battle-for-chinese-hearts-and-minds-in-flushing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Kil2016>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/nyregion/falun-gong-queens-federal-lawsuit.html?=supchina|title=Born on a Queens Street, a Battle Over Falun Gong Goes to Court|author=Corey Kilgannon|publisher=New York Times|date=2016-06-28|accessdate=2017-02-01|archive-date=2018-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203183105/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/nyregion/falun-gong-queens-federal-lawsuit.html?=supchina|dead-url=no}}</ref>。法輪功方面則認為該組織和[[中華人民共和國政府|北京當局]]有密切聯繫，係其爪牙。全球華人反邪教聯盟和法輪功方面均指責對方對己方進行了威脅或攻擊<ref name=Kil2011/>。2016年，法輪功支持者以「妨害宗教自由」為名在紐約起訴全球華人反邪教聯盟<ref name=Kil2016/><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/nyregion/falun-gong-queens-federal-lawsuit.html |title=Born on a Queens Street, a Battle Over Falun Gong Goes to Court |last=Kilgannon |first=Corey |date=2016-06-29 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2021-12-09 |language=en-US |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2022-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419025200/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/nyregion/falun-gong-queens-federal-lawsuit.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://casetext.com/case/jingrong-v-chinese-anti-cult-world-alliance-2 |title=Jingrong v. Chinese Anti-Cult World All., 311 F. Supp. 3d 514 |3=Casetext Search + Citator |accessdate=2021-12-09 |archive-date=2021-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210054604/https://casetext.com/case/jingrong-v-chinese-anti-cult-world-alliance-2/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/judge-sets-stage-falun-gong-091950948.html |title=Judge Sets Stage for Falun Gong's Religious Bias Case Against 'Anti-Cult' Group |accessdate=2021-12-09 |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210025737/https://www.yahoo.com/news/judge-sets-stage-falun-gong-091950948.html }}</ref>。

